{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"90dd069a18","title":"四言诗·戏改江沧”《别赋》","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"39a0626bc6","index":0,"year":1939,"month":7,"day":null,"articleId":"90dd069a18"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji13","name":"毛泽东全集第13卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji13.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji13":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"dd41978cfe","type":"paragraph","text":"四言诗·戏改江沧”《别赋》","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji13","articleId":"90dd069a18"},{"id":"35a9d62f5a","type":"paragraph","text":"（1939年7月）春草碧的色，春水绿波。送君延安，回","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji13","articleId":"90dd069a18"},{"id":"8c3ad6210f","type":"paragraph","text":"快如之何！码[1]江湾（444-505），需朝架代文学家，字文通，济阳考城（今河南兰考东）人。历仕宋、齐、梁三代。梁代时官至金紫光源大夫。少驱贫好学，早年即以文章著名，皖年才思衰退，所作诗文不如前期，人谓“江郎才尽”。诗歌多拟古之作。贰以《恨》《别默》最为有名。原有集，巴做供，后人辑有《江文通策》[2]碧，青绿色。[3]君，你。延安，当时中共中央所在地。送君延安，在廷安送别奔赴沈日前线或赴全国各地从事革命工作的同志。[4]快，快活，舒畅。之，这里是语助词，无实义。如之何，即如何，怎么样。快如之何，快活得怎么样。犹言快活极了！","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji13","articleId":"90dd069a18"}],"page":{"id":"16402d6bf3","publicationId":"maoquanji13","articleId":"90dd069a18","start":493,"end":493}}}},"__N_SSG":true}